title: MS Office Enterprise 2007 SP3 Visio Project SharePoint 03/2016
description:
Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007 SP3 Visio Project SharePoint en-US March 2016

About this release

*** Info

- Channel: Professional
- Level: SP3 for all components
- Architecture: 32-bit, do not ask for 64-bit version, there is none
- Language: English (United States)
- Proofing tools: English, French, Spanish
- Version: 12.0.4518.1014

*** OS requirements: Windows XP to 10, 32-bit/64-bit

Includes
- Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007 SP3 (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, Publisher, Access, InfoPath, Visio Viewer, Communicator, Groove, OneNote)
- Microsoft Office Visio 2007 Professional SP3
- Microsoft Office Project 2007 Professional SP3
- Microsoft Office SharePoint Designer 2007 SP3

*** Integrated updates: Until March 08, 2016

*** Installation

- Mount / burn / extract
- Install Office / Visio / Project / SharePoint Designer (no keys required, these were added to the setup files)
- Install Office File Validation + Visual Studio for Office Runtime (required) from folder "Run after install"
- Customize your installation with included Add-ins: Classic Menu for Office 2007 v7.50, FileFormatConverters, PowerPointViewer, SaveAsPDFandXPS, Wordview

Please be nice, don't be selfish, seed for a while ...
Thanks !
